@startuml
title Lean Verification Build Pipeline

actor Author
participant "MDX content" as MDX
participant "Lean files" as Lean
participant "lake build" as Lake
participant "lean-query.lean" as Query
participant "generate-lean-graph.ts" as Graph
participant "validate-lean-diff.ts" as Diff
participant "generate-content-index.ts" as Index

Author -> MDX: writes pedagogy + leanId
Author -> Lean: writes formal theorem/proof
Lean -> Lake: compile
Lake --> Lean: verified environment
Lean -> Query: export declarations/deps/proof blocks
Query -> Graph: raw JSON
Graph -> Diff: lean_graph.json
MDX -> Diff: metadata + stepTacticMap
Diff --> Author: divergence report
Graph -> Index: lean verification data
MDX -> Index: content metadata
Index --> Author: contentIndex.json with leanVerified
@enduml
